<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Setter Soft</title>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="calc-container">
        <div class="head">
            <h1><span>Calculadora </span>de ingresos orgánico</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="range">
            <div class="range_slider">
                <input type="range" id="followersCount" min="1000" max="1000000" step="1000" value="100000">
            </div>
            <div class="range_info">
                <label>Número de seguidores</label>
                <br>
                <span id="followersCountText">100000</span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="range">
            <div class="range_slider">
                <input type="range" id="followersChats" min="0.5" max="30" value="1" step="0.5">
            </div>
            <div class="range_info">
                <label>Porcentaje de chats</label>
                <br>
                <span id="followersChatsText">5%</span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="range">
            <div class="range_slider">
                <input type="range" id="bookingRatio" min="5" max="100" value="5" step="5">
            </div>
            <div class="range_info">
                <label>Ratio de reuniones</label>
                <br>
                <span id="bookingRatioText">5%</span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="range">
            <div class="range_slider">
                <input type="range" id="ticketSpend" min="100" max="20000" value="100" step="100">
            </div>
            <div class="range_info">
                <label>Ticket promedio</label>
                <br>
                <span id="ticketSpendText"><%=currency%> 100</span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="range">
            <div class="range_slider">
                <input type="range" id="leadCloseRatioRange" min="1" max="100" value="1" step="1">
            </div>
            <div class="range_info">
                <label>Ratio de cierre</label>
                <br>
                <span id="leadCloseRatioText">1%</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="result-calc-container">
        <!-- Table (first row title) and (second row result) -->
        <table>
            <tr>
                <th>LEADS</th>
                <th>REUNIONES</th>
                <th>VENTAS</th>
                <th>INGRESOS</th>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td id="resultLeads">1000</td>
                <td id="resultAgendas">200</td>
                <td id="resultVentas">10</td>
                <td id="resultGanancia"><%=currency%> 5000</td>
            </tr>
        </table>
        <div class="results">
            <div class="item">
                <label translate="no">Leads</label>
                <span id="mResultLeads">1000</span>
            </div>
            <div class="item">
                <label>Reuniones</label>
                <span id="mResultAgendas">200</span>
            </div>
            <div class="item">
                <label>Ventas</label>
                <span id="mResultVentas">10</span>
            </div>
            <div class="item">
                <label>Ingresos</label>
                <span id="mResultGanancia"><%=currency%> 5000</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <hr id="calc_separator">

    <div class="content">
        <div class="guarantee-banner">
            <div class="left-side">
                <h2>¿Qué tal una <span>garantía de devolución del 100% del dinero?</span></h2>
                <p>¿A quién más conoces que ponga eso por escrito?</p>
                <p>Si no ve un retorno de la inversión del 200% al trabajar con nosotros, le daremos todo su dinero sin preguntar. ¡Y te quedarás con el sistema!</p>
            </div>
            <div class="right-side">
                <div class="guarantee-logo">
                    <img src="https://images.leadconnectorhq.com/image/f_webp/q_80/r_1200/u_https://assets.cdn.filesafe.space/nCiFSON597KefWHupKoA/media/64a737281e4e7ba4f01246ec.png"
                        alt="">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        <div class="footer-container">
            <span class="rightReserved">© 2023 SetterSoft. All rights reserved.</span>
            <span class="emailAccount">support@settersoft.com</span>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

<style>
